            "text": "Item"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " - I gave Daniel this for Christmas, but it has ended up being more of a gift for myself. Oops! It is the "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
